TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: -- all component type Catalogue item SELECT DISTINCT item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID, item.PROD_MASTER_SRC_ID, item.PROD_CD, item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_TYPE_CD, item.DATA_SRC_ID, item.PROD_INTRNL_NM, --item.EFF_START_DT, item.EFF_END_DT, pc.sale_eff_start_dt,pc.sale_eff_end_dt, pc.SERVICE_TYPE_CD, --UPPER (pdesc.LANG_CD) AS PROD_DESC_LANG_CD, pdesc.PROD_DESC, --UPPER (pname.LANG_CD) AS PROD_NM_LANG_CD, pname.PROD_NM FROM PRODUCT_CATALOGUE_ITEM item JOIN PRODUCT_COMPONENT pc ON item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = PC.prod_cmpnt_id LEFT OUTER JOIN PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION pdesc ON (item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pdesc.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID AND pdesc.Prod_Desc_Purps_Cd = 'DE' AND UPPER (pdesc.lang_cd) = 'EN' AND (pdesc.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR pdesc.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND pdesc.EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE ) LEFT OUTER JOIN PRODUCT_NAME pname ON (item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pname.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID AND pname.PROD_NM_PURPS_CD = 'DE' AND UPPER (pname.lang_cd) = 'EN' AND (pname.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR pname.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND pname.EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE ) WHERE item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_TYPE_CD IN ('CMP') AND ( (item.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR item.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND item.Eff_Start_Dt < SYSDATE) AND ( pc.sale_eff_start_dt < SYSDATE --AND (pc.sale_eff_end_dt IS NULL OR pc.sale_eff_end_dt > SYSDATE) ) union all -- all Catalogue item (OFF,SPC,PPL) SELECT DISTINCT item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID, item.PROD_MASTER_SRC_ID, item.PROD_CD, item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_TYPE_CD, item.DATA_SRC_ID, item.PROD_INTRNL_NM, item.EFF_START_DT, item.EFF_END_DT, '' as service_type_cd, --UPPER (pdesc.LANG_CD) AS PROD_DESC_LANG_CD, pdesc.PROD_DESC, --UPPER (pname.LANG_CD) AS PROD_NM_LANG_CD, pname.PROD_NM FROM PRODUCT_CATALOGUE_ITEM item LEFT OUTER JOIN PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION pdesc ON (item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pdesc.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID AND pdesc.Prod_Desc_Purps_Cd = 'DE' AND UPPER (pdesc.lang_cd) = 'EN' AND (pdesc.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR pdesc.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND pdesc.EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE ) LEFT OUTER JOIN PRODUCT_NAME pname ON (item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pname.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID AND pname.PROD_NM_PURPS_CD = 'DE' AND UPPER (pname.lang_cd) = 'EN' AND (pname.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR pname.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND pname.EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE ) WHERE item.PROD_CATLG_ITM_TYPE_CD IN ('OFF', 'SPC','PPL') AND ( (item.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR item.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND item.Eff_Start_Dt < SYSDATE)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT tmp3.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID, tmp3.PROD_CD, tmp3.eff_start_dt, tmp3.eff_end_dt, tmp3.PROD_CATEGORY_TYPE_CD, tmp3.acquisition_Type, tmp3.model_name, tmp3.PURCHASE_PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD, tmp3.PURCHASE_CHARGE_TYPE_CD, tmp3.PURCHASE_PRICE, tmp3.RENTAL_PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD, tmp3.RENTAL_CHARGE_TYPE_CD, tmp3.RENTAL_PRICE, tmp3.LATE_RENTAL_PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD, tmp3.LATE_RENTAL_CHARGE_TYPE_CD, tmp3.LATE_RENTAL_PRICE, tmp4.PROD_DESC_LANG_CD, Tmp4.Prod_Desc FROM (SELECT acqType.acquisition_Type, model.model_name, pci.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID, pci.PROD_CD, pc.PROD_CATEGORY_TYPE_CD, pci.eff_start_dt, pci.eff_end_dt, pcp.PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD AS PURCHASE_PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD, pcp.CHARGE_TYPE_CD AS PURCHASE_CHARGE_TYPE_CD, pcp.PRICE_AMT AS PURCHASE_PRICE, rtp.PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD AS RENTAL_PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD, rtp.CHARGE_TYPE_CD AS RENTAL_CHARGE_TYPE_CD, rtp.PRICE_AMT AS RENTAL_PRICE, lrp.PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD AS LATE_RENTAL_PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD, lrp.CHARGE_TYPE_CD AS LATE_RENTAL_CHARGE_TYPE_CD, lrp.PRICE_AMT AS LATE_RENTAL_PRICE FROM (SELECT * FROM product_catalogue_item WHERE PROD_CATLG_ITM_TYPE_CD = 'EQP' AND (EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE --AND PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID FROM market_offer_item) ) pci, (SELECT * FROM product_category WHERE EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE AND (EFF_END_DT IS NULL OR EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE)) pc, (SELECT * FROM PRODUCT_ITEM_CATEGORY_ASGNMT WHERE EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE AND EFF_END_DT IS NULL OR EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE) pia, PRODUCT_CHARACTERISTIC pch, (SELECT * FROM product_price WHERE PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD = 'PURCHASE' AND EFF_START_TS < SYSDATE AND (EFF_END_TS IS NULL OR EFF_END_TS > SYSDATE)) pcp, (SELECT * FROM product_price WHERE PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD = 'RENT' AND EFF_START_TS < SYSDATE AND (EFF_END_TS IS NULL OR EFF_END_TS > SYSDATE)) rtp, (SELECT prod_catlg_itm_id, default_Val_txt acquisition_Type FROM PRODUCT_CHARACTERISTIC WHERE prod_charstc_intrnl_cd = 'acquisitionType') acqType, (SELECT prod_catlg_itm_id, default_Val_txt MODEL_NAME FROM PRODUCT_CHARACTERISTIC WHERE prod_charstc_intrnl_cd = 'Model') model, (SELECT * FROM product_price WHERE PROD_PRICE_TYPE_CD = 'LATE_RETURN_FEE' AND EFF_START_TS < SYSDATE AND (EFF_END_TS IS NULL OR EFF_END_TS > SYSDATE)) lrp WHERE pci.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pcp.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID(+) AND pci.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = rtp.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID(+) AND pci.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = lrp.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID(+) AND pci.prod_catlg_itm_id = acqType.prod_catlg_itm_id(+) AND pci.prod_catlg_itm_id = model.prod_catlg_itm_id(+) AND pci.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pia.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID AND pia.PROD_CATEGORY_ID = pc.PROD_CATEGORY_ID AND pia.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pch.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID) tmp3 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT pc.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID, UPPER (pd.LANG_CD) AS PROD_DESC_LANG_CD, pd.PROD_NM AS Prod_Desc FROM PRODUCT_CATALOGUE_ITEM pc, PRODUCT_NAME pd WHERE (pc.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR pc.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND pc.EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE AND (pd.EFF_END_DT > SYSDATE OR pd.EFF_END_DT IS NULL) AND pd.EFF_START_DT < SYSDATE AND pc.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID = pd.PROD_CATLG_ITM_ID AND Pd.Prod_Nm_Purps_Cd = 'DE') Tmp4 ON (Tmp3.Prod_Catlg_Itm_Id = Tmp4.Prod_Catlg_Itm_Id)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: WITH active_prod_relation AS ( -- -- Get all active product relationship as of today -- SELECT pr.prod_base_catlg_itm_id, pr.prod_reln_type_cd, pr.prod_catlg_itm_id, -- PARENT pr.prod_catlg_itm_id parent_prod_catlg_itm_id, parentcat.prod_catlg_itm_type_cd parent_prod_catlg_itm_type_cd, parentcat.prod_cd parent_prod_cd, parentcat.prod_intrnl_nm parent_prod_intrnl_nm, parentcmp.service_type_cd parent_component_svc_type_cd, -- CHILD pr.rel_prod_catlg_itm_id child_prod_catlg_itm_id, childcat.prod_catlg_itm_type_cd child_prod_catlg_itm_type_cd, childcat.prod_cd child_prod_cd, childcat.prod_intrnl_nm child_prod_intrnl_nm, childcmp.service_type_cd child_component_svc_type_cd, --relation pr.eff_start_dt reln_eff_start_dt, pr.eff_end_dt reln_eff_end_dt, pr.reln_optional_cd, pr.reln_min_allowed_qty, pr.reln_max_allowed_qty, pr.prod_reln_rsn_cd FROM product_relation pr, product_catalogue_item parentcat, product_catalogue_item childcat, product_component parentcmp, product_component childcmp WHERE (TRUNC (pr.eff_start_dt) <= TRUNC (SYSDATE)) AND (pr.eff_end_dt IS NULL OR pr.eff_end_dt > TRUNC (SYSDATE)) AND pr.prod_catlg_itm_id = parentcat.prod_catlg_itm_id(+) AND pr.rel_prod_catlg_itm_id = childcat.prod_catlg_itm_id(+) AND pr.prod_catlg_itm_id = parentcmp.prod_cmpnt_id(+) AND pr.rel_prod_catlg_itm_id = childcmp.prod_cmpnt_id(+)), offer_base_catlg -- oms offer id AS ( -- -- Get all offers -- SELECT DISTINCT tmp3.prod_catlg_itm_id "OFFER" FROM (SELECT pc1.prod_catlg_itm_id, pc1.prod_master_src_id, pc1.prod_cd, pc1.prod_catlg_itm_type_cd, pc1.data_src_id, pc1.prod_intrnl_nm, pc1.eff_start_dt, pc1.eff_end_dt FROM product_catalogue_item pc1 WHERE pc1.prod_catlg_itm_type_cd IN ('OFF') AND (pc1.eff_end_dt > SYSDATE OR pc1.eff_end_dt IS NULL) AND pc1.eff_start_dt < SYSDATE --AND pc1.prod_catlg_itm_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT prod_catlg_itm_id FROM market_offer_item) ) tmp3 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CASE WHEN tmp1.prod_catlg_itm_id IS NULL THEN tmp2.prod_catlg_itm_id ELSE tmp1.prod_catlg_itm_id END AS prod_catlg_itm_id, tmp1.prod_desc_lang_cd, tmp1.prod_desc, tmp2.prod_nm_lang_cd, tmp2.prod_nm FROM (SELECT pc.prod_catlg_itm_id, UPPER (pd.lang_cd) AS prod_desc_lang_cd, pd.prod_desc FROM product_catalogue_item pc, product_description pd WHERE (pc.eff_end_dt > SYSDATE OR pc.eff_end_dt IS NULL) AND pc.eff_start_dt < SYSDATE AND (pd.eff_end_dt > SYSDATE OR pd.eff_end_dt IS NULL) AND pd.eff_start_dt < SYSDATE AND pc.prod_catlg_itm_id = pd.prod_catlg_itm_id AND pd.prod_desc_purps_cd = 'DE') tmp1 FULL OUTER JOIN (SELECT pc.prod_catlg_itm_id, UPPER (pn.lang_cd) AS prod_nm_lang_cd, pn.prod_nm FROM product_catalogue_item pc, product_name pn WHERE (pc.eff_end_dt > SYSDATE OR pc.eff_end_dt IS NULL) AND pc.eff_start_dt < SYSDATE AND (pn.eff_end_dt > SYSDATE OR pn.eff_end_dt IS NULL) AND pn.eff_start_dt < SYSDATE AND pc.prod_catlg_itm_id = pn.prod_catlg_itm_id AND pn.prod_nm_purps_cd = 'DE') tmp2 ON tmp1.prod_catlg_itm_id = tmp2.prod_catlg_itm_id AND tmp1.prod_desc_lang_cd = tmp2.prod_nm_lang_cd) tmp4 ON (tmp3.prod_catlg_itm_id = tmp4.prod_catlg_itm_id) -- WHERE tmp3.prod_catlg_itm_id IN (101412, 1219000) ), offer_ppl -- -- Get all PPL for offers -- AS (SELECT pr.prod_base_catlg_itm_id "OFFER", pr.parent_prod_catlg_itm_id, pr.child_prod_catlg_itm_id FROM active_prod_relation pr, offer_base_catlg obc WHERE pr.prod_reln_type_cd = 'OFF_PPL' AND pr.prod_base_catlg_itm_id = obc.offer), offer_spc -- -- Get all SPC for offers -- AS (SELECT DISTINCT obc.offer, pr.child_prod_catlg_itm_id "SPC" FROM offer_base_catlg obc, active_prod_relation pr WHERE pr.prod_reln_type_cd IN ('OFF_SPC') AND pr.prod_catlg_itm_id = obc.offer), smaller_pr -- -- Create a smaller subset of active product relationship to speed up the connected by SQL -- AS (SELECT pr.* FROM active_prod_relation pr WHERE pr.prod_reln_type_cd IN ('OFF_SPC', 'SPC_CMP') UNION SELECT pr2.* FROM active_prod_relation pr2 WHERE pr2.prod_reln_type_cd = 'CMP_CMP' AND pr2.prod_base_catlg_itm_id IN (SELECT spc FROM offer_spc) UNION SELECT pr3.* FROM active_prod_relation pr3 WHERE pr3.prod_reln_type_cd IN ('SPC_PPL', 'CMP_PPL') AND (parent_prod_catlg_itm_id, child_prod_catlg_itm_id) IN (SELECT parent_prod_catlg_itm_id, child_prod_catlg_itm_id FROM offer_ppl) ), result_0 -- -- Going thru the hierarchy starting with offers -- AS ( SELECT CONNECT_BY_ROOT prod_catlg_itm_id "OFFER", LEVEL "NODE_LEVEL", SYS_CONNECT_BY_PATH (pr.prod_catlg_itm_id, '/') || '/' || child_prod_catlg_itm_id "NODE_PATH", SYS_CONNECT_BY_PATH (pr.prod_base_catlg_itm_id, '/') "BASE_PROD_PATH", pr.* FROM smaller_pr pr START WITH pr.prod_catlg_itm_id IN (SELECT offer FROM offer_base_catlg) CONNECT BY NOCYCLE PRIOR pr.child_prod_catlg_itm_id = pr.prod_catlg_itm_id), result_1 -- -- Get the 2nd item in node_path as SPC -- E.g. SPC=101096, offer=1219000 in node path /1219000/101096/101097/101402/101075/101076 -- AS (SELECT r.*, REGEXP_SUBSTR (node_path, '[^/]+', 1, 2) "SPC" FROM result_0 r), result -- -- For CMP, all base_prod must be = SPC, except the first node -- For PPL, all base_prod must be = SPC, except the first node and last node + Rule 3 -- AS (SELECT DISTINCT r.* FROM result_1 r WHERE r.child_prod_catlg_itm_type_cd = 'CMP' AND REGEXP_REPLACE (base_prod_path, '/' || spc) = '/' || offer UNION SELECT DISTINCT r.* FROM result_1 r, offer_ppl op WHERE r.child_prod_catlg_itm_type_cd = 'PPL' AND r.offer = op.offer AND r.parent_prod_catlg_itm_id = op.parent_prod_catlg_itm_id AND r.child_prod_catlg_itm_id = op.child_prod_catlg_itm_id AND REGEXP_REPLACE (base_prod_path, '/' || spc) = '/' || r.offer || '/' || prod_base_catlg_itm_id UNION SELECT DISTINCT r.* FROM result_1 r WHERE child_prod_catlg_itm_type_cd NOT IN ('CMP', 'PPL')) -- SELECT * FROM result r ORDER BY offer, node_level, prod_reln_type_cd, parent_prod_catlg_itm_id, child_prod_catlg_itm_id
